{"service_name": "Information security strategy", "service_id": "4919632020373504", "company_name": "Portcullis Computer Security Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Portcullis Computer Security Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Information security strategy\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Information security is a complex, evolving landscape as are many organisations themselves. A strategy is required to ensure that an organisation\u2019s requirements are being understood and met, both today and in the future. Portcullis has assisted many organisations in clarifying their requirements and developing a strategy to meet these.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Strategies cover all aspects; from staffing and policy to technical\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Linked to business and compliance requirements\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Focus is on allowing an organisation to deliver\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Making security an enabler, not a blocker\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ensuring that solutions are \u2018future proof\u2019\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Able to lead and support projects such as this\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     SC and DV Team personnel where required\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Full SC project management wrap around\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Dedicated editorial team to ensure the highest quality deliverables\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Offering a secure environment for delivery of specific projects\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Portcullis is an ISO 27001 certified organisation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Excellent track-record of delivering services to Government\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     All projects are driven by pre-agreed deliverables (KPIs)\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3800 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Termination costs apply\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92928/4919632020373504-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92928/4919632020373504-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92928/4919632020373504-service-definition-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92928/4919632020373